{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/data-deletion/layout,_N_T_/data-deletion/page,_N_T_/data-deletion"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/data-deletion/__PAGE__","/data-deletion","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--tuiwCswFgVYJS7c5fP1SU--><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.dbea232f.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.853070df.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" imageSrcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 2x\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/8d8e0b2ffed2c870.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/bb8f42ac442d7a63.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/82abf2d65f5428ae.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/aee6c7720838f8a2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3b2ed5fb7ad1f280.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-8fa6a74498c6fa50.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/57565527b8f329ce.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/d2be314c3ece3fbe.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/b4872826d9ffb447.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Data Deletion | Lensically</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"How to delete your Lensically account and what data is removed.\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://lensically.com/data-deletion\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0b3bf435.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white text-black\"><main class=\"mx-auto flex w-full max-w-4xl flex-col gap-8 px-6 py-16 sm:px-8\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Lensically logo\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-16 w-16 rounded-md\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flensically-logo-white-with-black-bg.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Lensically</span></a><div class=\"space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500\">Public Data Deletion Information</p><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900\">How to delete your Lensically account</h1><p class=\"max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">Lensically provides self-serve account deletion from the authenticated account settings area. Deletion is permanent and removes the account data associated with your use of the application.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-rose-900\">Deleting your Lensically account permanently removes associated user data from the system. This action cannot be undone.</div><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Official public review URL</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">The canonical public data deletion instructions for provider review are available at<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-slate-900 underline\" href=\"https://lensically.com/data-deletion\">https://lensically.com/data-deletion</a>.</p></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Delete your account</h2><ol class=\"mt-4 list-decimal space-y-3 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\"><li>Sign in to your Lensically account.</li><li>Open the account settings page.</li><li>Select the delete account action.</li><li>Confirm the permanent deletion prompt.</li><li>After confirmation, Lensically runs the deletion process and removes your account from the system.</li></ol></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">What data is removed</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">When account deletion completes, Lensically permanently removes the account and related application records tied to that user, including:</p><ul class=\"mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\"><li>Your Lensically user account record</li><li>Active sessions and authentication cookies</li><li>Connected OAuth provider linkages</li><li>Email verification and password reset tokens</li><li>Usage tracking records associated with your account</li><li>Scheduled posts stored for your account</li></ul></section><section class=\"rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Need help?</h2><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">The related public privacy policy used for provider review is available at<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-slate-900 underline\" href=\"/privacy\">https://lensically.com/privacy</a>.</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">If you cannot access your account and need assistance with deletion, contact Lensically support and include the email address associated with your account.</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900\">Support: <a class=\"underline\" href=\"mailto:support@lensically.com\">support@lensically.com</a></p></section></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/bb8f42ac442d7a63.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83917,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/57565527b8f329ce.js\\\"],\\\"AuthProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/d2be314c3ece3fbe.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/ff1a16fafef87110.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/d2be314c3ece3fbe.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/57565527b8f329ce.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/b4872826d9ffb447.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[5500,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/57565527b8f329ce.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/b4872826d9ffb447.js\\\"],\\\"Image\\\"]\\ne:I[68027,[],\\\"default\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/8d8e0b2ffed2c870.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.dbea232f.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.853070df.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"tuiwCswFgVYJS7c5fP1SU\\\",\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"data-deletion\\\"],\\\"q\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"data-deletion\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/chunks/8d8e0b2ffed